    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK205">
<l>ilameṉṟu tīyavai ceyyaṟka ceyyi</l>
<l>ṉilaṉāku maṟṟum peyarttu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Commit not evil, saying, "I am poor": if you do, you will become poorer still.</l>
            </lg>
